{"tid":2353580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡將會容許警方利用當地感染追綜app調查刑事案","createTime":"2021-01-05T00:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T04:47:21.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3a487fba46c2c5a6e6cb1bc59c5d17d820b09340","tid":2353580,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:19:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.engadget.com/singapore-tracetogether-police-225552941.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.engadget.com%2Fsingapore-tracetogether-police-225552941.html&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuObhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=5f8e3efd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.engadget.com/singapore-tracetogether-police-225552941.html</a><br />\n<br />\nIn an update the government made to the platform&rsquo;s privacy policy on Monday, it added a paragraph about how police can use data collected through the platform. &ldquo;TraceTogether data may be used in circumstances where citizen safety and security is or has been affected,&rdquo; the new paragraph states. &ldquo;Authorized Police officers may invoke Criminal Procedure Code (CPC) powers to request users to upload their TraceTogether data for criminal investigations.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nPrevious versions of the privacy policy made no mention of the fact police could access any data collected by the app; in fact, the website used to say, &ldquo;data will only be used for COVID-19 contact tracing.&rdquo; The government added the paragraph after Singapore&rsquo;s opposition party asked the Minister of State for Home Affairs if police could use the data for criminal investigations. &quot;We do not preclude the use of TraceTogether data in circumstances where citizens' safety and security is or has been affected, and this applies to all other data as well,&quot; said Minister Desmond Tan. <br />\n<br />\nWhat&rsquo;s happening in Singapore is an example of the exact type of potential privacy nightmare that experts warned might happen with centralized digital contact tracing efforts. Worse, a loss of trust in the privacy of data could push people further away from contact tracing efforts altogether, putting everyone at more risk."},{"pid":"4262591f18353189d0597c27327dbe183cf45ac0","tid":2353580,"uid":51271,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:20:16.000Z","msg":"好快香港都會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021296ce781dcde3f028679298f8f86342d0c87e","tid":2353580,"uid":388639,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"4262591f18353189d0597c27327dbe183cf45ac0","tid":2353580,"uid":51271,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:20:16.000Z","msg":"好快香港都會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:21:39.000Z","msg":"香港班狗就算唔容許都會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cf1fd42e63b2e4978462215e6bb9f2439120ad","tid":2353580,"uid":14918,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:28:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/tracetogether/id1498276074?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Ftracetogether%2Fid1498276074%3Fl%3Den&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuObhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=8b526719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/tracetogether/id1498276074?l=en</a><br />\n<br />\n香港原來抄坡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5db1f6be40c4c9e4fff609c1f99345714b1a73","tid":2353580,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:32:36.000Z","msg":"唔犯法咪得"},{"pid":"011fe81d75d5a8324992a90db60ea0092074fd60","tid":2353580,"uid":288304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4262591f18353189d0597c27327dbe183cf45ac0","tid":2353580,"uid":5127